            "description": "The headquarter of Microsoft Central and Eastern Europe had an open position for the \u2018Partner Skills Development Manager\u2019 and \u2018Partner Channel Marketing Manager\u2019. During five months I took over both responsibilities at the same time on an ad interim basis. I was able to grow a sense of PLDS community across the area, resulting in a higher adoption rate of best practices. Through 1:1 consultancy of the low performing subs I helped them to focus on the right activities. The main PLDS scorecard item, PSRI metric, increased immensely resulting in CEE area becoming the best performing area worldwide. CEE became the best performing area worldwide on the Jumpstart program as well. This was my most important responsibility as Partner Channel Marketing Manager.",
